reviewText:
Elvis Presley 25th Anniversary. The Definitive Collection

16 One Hour Episodes On 8 VHS

Includes:
~ The Memphis Years/The Television Years
~ The Hollywood Years 1/The Hollywood Years 2
~ The Army years/The Memphis Mafia
~ Elvis & Prescilla/Elvis & The Colonel
~ The Many Loves Of Elvis/The Intimate Loves Of Elvis
~ The Comeback/The Vegas Years
~ A Man And His Music/The Spiritual Soul Of Elvis
~ Elvis Is Gone/All The King's Disciples:The Fans
